", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"state\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Already, it has been severely criticised by descendants of the tower's designer Gustave Eiffel, as well as conservation groups.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Eiffel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gustave Eiffel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Eiffel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustave_Eiffel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"descendants\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"conservation groups\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of last month, workers removed the 30-tonne steel rings that were first installed in June between the first and second floors of the tower.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"last month\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"the 30-tonne steel rings\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"the first and second floors\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"the tower\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hidalgo has campaigned for lighter, less prominent, versions of the originals to be installed in their place.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hidalgo\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"lighter, less prominent, versions\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 958}, {\"ngram\": \"the originals\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"their place\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But even this toned-down proposal is too much for sceptics, some of whom are also bitter political enemies of Hidalgo.\", \"fr