he central government\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dati told the daily Le Parisien that the tower's current status as an ordinary listed monument was no longer sufficient.\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Parisien\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dati\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2053}, {\"ngram\": \"the tower's current status\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"an ordinary listed monument\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only its inclusion on the French state's top heritage list, reserved for sites of national importance, would offer \\\"true protection\\\", she argued.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2196, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9680101127868359, \"rank\": 0.016904459148091515, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only its inclusion\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"sites\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"national importance\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"true protection\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Any work done on a building or monument with full heritage status requires the approval of the regional prefect, who answers to the government, or other state-run agencies.\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Any work\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"a building\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"monument\", \"from\": 2